{"type": "article", "id": 45403, "title": "优衣库进军西班牙，以及，Burberry 的摄影展值得一看 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-09-21T03:29:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 16038, "name": "BAPE"}, {"id": 44224, "name": "Livestock"}, {"id": 3865, "name": "adidas Originals"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 16641, "name": "太平鸟"}, {"id": 3110, "name": "D&G"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170921110900XfayYDdkUOrIJpZ3.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/477155\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>优衣库进军 Zara 大本营，在西班牙开店</b></a> | 9 月 20 日，优衣库在西班牙的第一家店开幕。这家店位于巴塞罗那的一栋始建于 20 世纪初的建筑内，占地面积 1730 平方米。西班牙是优衣库在英国、法国、德国、比利时、俄罗斯之后的第六个欧洲国家市场，优衣库计划在 11 月 9 日在巴塞罗那开设第二家店。</p><p><a href=\"http://fashionmagazine.it/ItemByCategory.aspx?ItemID=82104\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Dolce&amp;Gabbana 净利润暴涨，年销售额达 13 亿欧元</b></a> | 在截止至 2017 年 3 月 31 日的 12 个月内，Dolce&amp;Gabbana 的销售额同比上涨 9.6%，至 13 亿欧元，净利润暴涨了近四倍，达 8000 万欧元。意大利仍是 Dolce&amp;Gabbana 的主要市场，占有 24% 的销售额，欧洲其它地区为 27%，美洲 13%，日本 6%。</p><p><a href=\"http://finance.ifeng.com/a/20170921/15685895_0.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>太平鸟与天猫达成战略合作，目标三年内线上销售破百亿</b></a> | 太平鸟与阿里巴巴昨天签了一份新零售战略合作，计划在品牌建设、大数据、消费者运营和线上线下全渠道融合等领域开展深入的战略合作，目标在 2020 年前实现线上销售额过百亿，整体销售额达 200 亿。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>9 月 18 日至 10 月 1 日，Burberry 在位于 Clerkenwell的全新秀场 Old Sessions House，举办了一场名为<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/477337\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <i>Here We Are</i> </a>的摄影展。这场展览以英国生活为主题，展出了超过 200 张照片，包括一些 Alasdair McLellan、ShirleyBaker 和 Ken Russell 从未公开过的作品。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110158yVeIAsUQ0dOzk1BP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110156ts6vYLxEMaKQrwjI.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.667151\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110156kO9AL67RJyqWlfpn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.563578\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211101583mq6Q94UAla7pHvb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.711250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>从 BMX 汲取灵感，BAPE 推出名为 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/bape-dirtrace-bmx-capsule\" rel=\"nofollow\">DIRTRACE</a> 的全新系列。该系列包括 BMX 单车、反光迷彩外套、多款印花 T 恤、帽子、杯子等多款单品，将于 9 月 30 日起在 BAPE 各大指定门店发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110239g71EvQqlm9KTPSsW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110249bqRPz1F5cIMDgmVT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110249cDmFiLNPHQ1YCIgW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211102491GQpPjoYMiuOBkVq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110249rDwZfOj4CFM3oWxz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110249cwf47mXd5eGCPHjn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110249BJ5CH7nSu9EzNv3M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110249CKdNgVtTSnBJDaPp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211103046N9BZLDUikXEzFP2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110301QBXYVpMUeOb1L9GP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110302DAhUGygF1iHRWLsJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110301TYE9QMRmtZ5XGge0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211103016i3ST1QVG9jBtgR8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110302Ioj6Zalv74T0tAKp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110303Hn6KTaPjiXR4Fs2f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110303xbWIBug0MiUpeRwX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110303sP1YrCAyBtz0d9SI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211103033lXwfN5zO1xQaMgY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110304jlVvHCXM0xUr8p6I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211103044FxA0XuHsalNgBUp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211103095uB1N6ihAdqSCPbk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110309s1vYEPzTIJBjARnN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110319GUcX7AzDuihw4oaR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110319mUNKcjBJoOirldeL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>各大品牌秋冬系列 lookbook 纷纷出炉，来看看都有哪些好看的： </p><p>纽约街头品牌<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/head-of-state-spring-summer-2018-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Head of State</a> 发布 Fulfilling All Righteousness 系列，灵感来自 Clic Clac Baby、Samuel Fosso、Malick Sidibe 以及 Seydou Keita 等知名非洲现代艺术家，用色挺大胆的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211104160WkP6mpbBj8KHE9R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110411lGhtuTmMLbvzHe9W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110413ZCjm4zKtvEScnOUo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211104053olu7Dk94KAW0JtV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110407E4qTufIUhQkMln9O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211104081FQzYsI65BaREUe7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110408HO40ZCGuDUjwQbYS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110410yJPhsw0rIxMNfAg3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110410FVSJDZbtasUduNr0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110411Cf7BjczX54TF1usM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110414iuPdrTOkaEbRsIB1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110414AhZlSX0xHvrFpC4L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092111041437rTtFy9fJ4QbLIk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211104151GsoU20Iv6RzghQl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211104147nxAHcyVvYLpeoDZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>喜欢工装风的话，加拿大名店<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/livestock-2017-fall-workwear-editorial\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Livestock </a>的 lookbook 是份不错的参考。这本特辑选用了来自 Garbstore、Carhartt WIP、Stan Ray、Alterior、adidas、Clarks Originals、Arc’teryx、Converse 等品牌最新单品。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110452x0jeoOkiJSNtWRu7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110452sLevBXCrQJ9UaEHb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110454lPCkAIGaxqzpQ4rd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211104543rS1efGT4qHPNC80.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110455zwYgB8xFtLQbNq1M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110455nWNkSZcu9ri8wjbJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110455PR5IvEfCZb0wpMui.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110456LOpegjA8yI9ChDtU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211104564kXKpCwlfGRm8enD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110456DRPTN7o45nxmaXU0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>adidas Originals 两款袜式中筒新鞋发售日期确定，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/adidas-originals-eqt-support-adv-winter-release-date\" rel=\"nofollow\">NMD XR1 Winter</a> 和 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/adidas-originals-nmd-xr1-winter-release-date\" rel=\"nofollow\">EQT Support ADV </a>将在 10 月 27 日同步登场。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110530aKANCSdEVrg4L3Qx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110530q3pATjHu9fYn0xbg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921110555pA21b0xiReDOLwzB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092111055238wC9ELh26KvJbMx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/477337\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd</a></p>"}